    <item>
      <title>中国疲软的货币正在推动其出口并招致批评</title>
      <link>https://www.nytimes.com/2025/12/07/business/china-rmb-currency.html</link>
      <description><![CDATA[中国的人民币汇率落后于主要贸易伙伴的货币，这使得中国的商品和服务变得便宜，并有助于推动出口。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.nytimes.com/2025/12/07/business/china-rmb-currency.html</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 08 Dec 2025 04:18:52 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>中国贸易顺差首次突破1万亿美元</title>
      <link>https://www.nytimes.com/2025/12/07/business/china-trade-surplus.html</link>
      <description><![CDATA[特朗普总统的关税不足以阻止中国的全球出口潮，中国在短短 11 个月内就突破了去年的纪录。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.nytimes.com/2025/12/07/business/china-trade-surplus.html</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 08 Dec 2025 04:15:17 GMT</pubDate>
